# Regression tests for #335 and #336 — compiler loop-context caps.
# #335: break #65+ in one loop emitted OP_LOOP_ENV_END without its jump
#       (double free at runtime). The executed break below is #65.
# #336: loops nested past the old MAX_LOOP_DEPTH (32) bound break to the
#       32nd loop's context (wrong jump target + stack corruption).
